      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total beauty! This car is in truly pristine, mint condition\u2014honestly, it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this ride since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. You really have to see it in person to believe how spotless it is! If you're looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the dealership stress, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
