    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in superlative condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 powerplant, equipped with high-pressure double-VANOS and six individual throttle bodies for an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain consists of a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission linked to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally optimized with documented subframe reinforcement and rides on a precise Bilstein B16 coilover system. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory luster with zero orange peel or swirl marks. This is a mechanically turn-key, concours-level specimen for the discerning purist.",
