      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. The exterior boasts a flawless, mirror-like finish, completely free of swirls or rock chips, having been professionally ceramic coated and strictly garage-kept. Inside, the cabin retains its factory-fresh scent, with supple, unmarked leather and pristine touchpoints that show zero signs of wear. Mechanically, this car is peerless; it comes with a complete, documented service history from authorized specialists, ensuring it drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Every electronic feature works perfectly, and the engine bay is clean enough to eat off. This is a rare opportunity to own a 'time capsule' example that has been pampered and preserved with obsessive attention to detail. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
