    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been kept in a climate-controlled garage and looks just as stunning as the day it rolled off the lot\u2014no scratches, no dings, just pure perfection! It drives like a dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been pampered and is ready for the road, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
