    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and optimized via Double VANOS. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a variable M-differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. This chassis has undergone comprehensive preventive maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, ensuring structural rigidity and mechanical longevity. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory luster with zero oxidation, while the suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing fresh bushings and OEM-spec Sachs dampers. A true purist\u2019s specimen with a clean title and documented service history.",
